24:["$","ul","ul-2",{"className":"space-y-2 mb-4 ml-4","children":["\n",["$","li","li-0",{"className":"text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed","children":[["$","strong","strong-0",{"className":"text-foreground font-semibold","children":"Price risk"}]," — you hold the underlying token. Bear markets destroy your portfolio value regardless of yield."]}],"\n",["$","li","li-1",{"className":"text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed","children":[["$","strong","strong-0",{"className":"text-foreground font-semibold","children":"Slashing"}]," — validator misbehavior can burn your stake (rare but non-zero, especially on smaller networks)."]}],"\n",["$","li","li-2",{"className":"text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed","children":[["$","strong","strong-0",{"className":"text-foreground font-semibold","children":"Lock-up"}]," — ETH unstaking takes days. Some chains lock for 21+ days. Capital is illiquid during drawdowns."]}],"\n",["$","li","li-3",{"className":"text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed","children":[["$","strong","strong-0",{"className":"text-foreground font-semibold","children":"Smart contract risk"}]," — liquid staking protocols (Lido, Rocket Pool) add a contract risk layer."]}],"\n",["$","li","li-4",{"className":"text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed","children":[["$","strong","strong-0",{"className":"text-foreground font-semibold","children":"Yield compression"}]," — as more people stake, rewards dilute. ETH has gone from 5%+ to 3.3% as ",["$","a","a-0",{"href":"https://coinlaw.io/eth-staking-statistics/","className":"text-primary underline underline-offset-2 hover:text-primary/80 transition-colors","target":"_blank","rel":"noopener noreferrer","children":"participation grew to 28% of supply"}],"."]}],"\n"]}]
