34:["$","p","p-27",{"className":"text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed mb-4","children":[["$","strong","strong-0",{"className":"text-foreground font-semibold","children":"Winner: Depends on risk tolerance."}]," Leverage amplifies returns but introduces liquidation risk. Zirodelta mitigates this with auto-deleverage (reduces positions rather than liquidating collateral)."]}]
